        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": [
        "1. Draw a line in a diagram from position (1, 3) to (2, 10) then to (6, 12) and finally to position\n",
        "(18, 20). (Mark each point with beautiful green colour and set the line colour to red and line\n",
        "style dotted)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "id": "7tLkb0iX-00K"
      }
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "xpoints=np.array([1,2,6,18])\n",
        "ypoints=np.array([3,10,12,20])\n",
        "plt.plot(xpoints,ypoints,color=\"red\",marker=\"o\",linestyle=\"dotted\",mec=\"g\",mfc=\"g\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],
